---
title: Caribbean Style Chicken Stew with Herby Ciabatta
description: We love good Chicken Stew with Garlicky Bread and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-style-chicken-stew-b4992b84-bccf0481.jpg
